content.text:
I don't have any memory of previous conversations. Each conversation with me starts fresh, and I don't have access to:

- Previous chat history
- Code or information you may have shared in earlier conversations
- Any context from past interactions

If you have code you'd like me to help with now, please share it again and I'll be happy to assist! You can:
- Paste it directly in your message
- Ask me to look at files in a project (I can read and modify files in the sandboxed environment)
- Describe what you need help with

What would you like to work on?
